✨ What a night to remember! ✨

On 31st May 2025, Mumbai witnessed the grandeur of the Rubaru Mr. India 2025 Grand Finale - a celebration of talent, confidence, and charisma. The evening featured an incredible swimwear round, showcasing stunning designs by Nidhi Munim, adding a edgy vibe to the event!

The show was beautifully directed by Karun Raman, making the night even more spectacular.

Swimwear by @house_of_nm
Show director @karunraman
Hmu = @sahil_anand_arora

Credits: @rubarumr.india and @pankajkharbandaa sir
